<F P=102>   TA2805191094 Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Hebrew 1800 GMT 28 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2805191094 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Israel Television Channel 1 Network 
in Hebrew 1800 GMT 28 May 94 </F>

<F P=105> Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Another incident between the IDF [Israel Defense 
Forces] and the Palestinian police occurred near the Erez 
checkpoint yesterday. Our military correspondent Alon Ben-David 
reports that an argument erupted between an IDF patrol and the 
Palestinian police, during which the Palestinian policemen 
cocked their weapons and aimed them at an Israeli officer. The 
Palestinians claim that the IDF soldiers cocked their weapons 
first, while the IDF soldiers claim the Palestinians threatened 
them without cause. The joint liaison and coordination 
committee launched an investigation into the incident. 

</TEXT>

