<H3> <TI>   Holds Talks With Sultan </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Holds Talks With Sultan </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   EA2805200594 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
in Arabic 1630 GMT 28 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA2805200594 </F>
<F P=104>  Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Network 
