<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Sanaa, 29 May (MENA)--Military sources in Sanaa have 
stated that Former Defense Minister Brigadier General Haytham 
Qasim Tahir, who was recently relieved of his post by President 
'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, was killed last week. These sources note 
