<F P=105> Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A responsible military source in the command of the 
Armed Forces of the Democratic Republic of Yemen has 
categorically denied in a statement to the Yemeni news agency, 
SABA', Aden, the reports carried by some foreign news agencies 
this evening, that the al-'Anad air base is under the control of 
the forces of the al-Ahmar gang. The source confirmed that the 
Armed Forces of the Democratic Republic of Yemen are in full 
control of the al-'Anad zone, including the air base. In its 
statement, the source pointed out that news agency 
correspondents visited the air base and confirmed that our 
forces were in control of the air base, and indicated this in 
voice and video reports. 

