<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shots Fired at Machinery Depot in Qatif Bloc </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA3105132294 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1200 GMT 31 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA3105132294 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Several shots were fired a short while ago at a 
heavy machinery depot near the settlement of Ganey Tal in the 
Qatif Bloc. There were no casualties. A soldier guarding the 
site returned fire and the security forces launched searches. 
  An investigation revealed that several bullets struck 
tractors and other equipment. A complaint was submitted to the 
regional liaision offices in Khan Yunus. 

