<F P=100> ARABIAN PENINSULA </F>
<F P=101> Saudi Arabia </F>
<H3> <TI>   King Fahd Undergoes Gallstone Surgery </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    King Fahd Undergoes Gallstone Surgery </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD3105201194 Riyadh Saudi Arabian Television Network in 
Arabic 1830 GMT 31 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3105201194 </F>
