<H4>    Tawr al-Bahah, al-'Abr Areas Purged </H4>

<F P=102> JN3105142694 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1200 GMT 31 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN3105142694 </F>
