purging of the remaining pockets which were controlled by the 
forces of apostasy and secession in the Lahij Governorate. He 
said that they have completed the purging of the Tawr al-Bahah 
District. He stressed that the important targets in the Aden 
Governorate are now within the range of the guns of the forces 
of legitimacy and unity. 
