<H3> <TI>   People's Assembly Committee Regrets Sudanese Measures </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    People's Assembly Committee Regrets Sudanese Measures </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC3105134094 Cairo Arab Republic of Egypt Radio Network in 
