<H3> <TI>   Warrant Issued for Muslim Brotherhood Guide </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Warrant Issued for Muslim Brotherhood Guide </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2805145394 Cairo AL-WAFD in Arabic 23 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> NC2805145394 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo AL-WAFD </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Imbabah District Prosecutor has ordered the 
arrest of Muslim Brotherhood General Guide Hamid Abu-al-Nasr. 
He is to be questioned about leaflets bearing his name that 
were distributed following the 'Id al-Fitr prayers the day 
