BFN 

  [Excerpt] The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] today released 73 
Palestinians prisoners who live in the Gaza Strip. Local Gazans 
are furious over the small number of people released and claim 
this is a violation of the Cairo agreement. Israel has so far 
released 2,000 prisoners, whereas it undertook to release 5,000 
in the agreement. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

