<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shots Fired at Policemen Guarding Jericho Synagogue </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shots Fired at Policemen Guarding Jericho Synagogue </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA3005055694 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 0400 GMT 30 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA3005055694 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In Jericho, several shots were fired last night 
from a moving car at Palestinian policemen on guard outside the 
Shalom 'Al Yisra'el Synagogue. No one was injured. A Qol 
Yisra'el reporter says the policemen reported the incident to a 
joint patrol, which stopped a suspicious car in connection with 
the incident. The investigation is continuing. 

</TEXT>

